	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_65484450">Is there an AI backlash, or is there a movement away from the marketing and towards the science?<br> <br>

Plus more public awareness of the historic overpromises, or let's just call it optimism, on the pace that science is able to turn AI theory into practical application.<br>
1950s: AI will beat a chess master in 10 years.<br>
1960s: AI will beat a chess master in 10 years.<br>
1970s: AI will beat a chess master in 10 years.<br>
1980s: AI will beat a chess master in 10 years.<br>
1990s: AI beats a chess master, we told you we would do it.<br><nobr> <wbr></nobr>:-)</div>
