Against individuals that would obviously be bad news but we're not going up against individuals we're going up against large companies that dominate markets. <br> <br>

Basically antitrust law enforcement is about having a referee for capitalism. So as soon as it looks like you're going to do something dodgy you're stopped from doing something do</div>
	</div>

